'''Jiizas: di Buk We Luuk Rait bout Im''' adawaiz kaal '''Luuk''' ah di toerd buk ah di Nyuu Testiment ina di Kristian [[Baibl|Baibl]]. It ah di longges out ah aala di fuor kyananikal buk dem weh dehn kaal Sinaptik Gaspl (Synoptic Gospels) weh taak bout di arijin, tiichinz, det, rezarekshan ahn asenshan ah [[Jiizas Krais|Jiizas Krais]] ([[Jesus|Jesus]]). <ref name=usccb.org>[http://www.usccb.org/bible/luke/0 "Luke - Introduction", United States Conference of Catholic Bishops website.]</ref> Dis ya buk no egzakli seh a Luuk rait ih, bot nof skola agrii seh dehn fain inof evidens ina it fi mek dem biliiv seh a im rait ih. Wahn ah di mieja difrans dem wid Luuk ahn di ada Sinaptik Gaspl dem iz dat it ah di ongl buk weh kom wid a falarop. Dis ya falarop niem [[''h''Ax a di Apasl|''h''Ax a di Apasl]] ahn nof skola kansida di tuu a dem togeda wen dem ah taak bout aida wahn. <ref name=Blueletterbible.org>[https://www.blueletterbible.org/study/intros/luke.cfm "The Gospel of Luke", Blue Letter Bible official website.]</ref> Luuk muosli fuokos pon salvieshan akaadn tu im andastandin ah di wil ah [[Gad|Gad]] bies aafa Im akshan dem chruout ischri. Ina dis ya buk, di ischri ah fos senchri [[Kristianiti|Kristianiti]] divaid op ina chrii stiej. Di fos tuu stiej dem taak bout wen di Mesaiya jos kom pon oert - fram im baan, tu wen im miit [[Jan di Baptis|Jan di Baptis]]. Di laas stiej fuokos pon di taim wen him wehn a tiich pon di oert, tu im det ahn rezarekshan. <ref name=tyndale.ca>[http://www.tyndale.ca/seminary/mtsmodular/reading-rooms/newt/luke "Gospel of Luke Reading Room", Tyndale Seminary.]</ref>

